title: Airport Enhancement Services 2.30+Credits
description:
What was new in AES 2.30:
When using the Followme, only the marshaller/dockingsystem of the destination Gate is active
Pushback switchable between "nose" and "tail" direction
New Neoplan Bus
New Fueltruck for apron positions
new staff for Cleaning, Water, Fuel and Loading vehicles
The loading process and entering passengers is not yet finished and will follow later.
